      <title>中国电池材料石墨出口受管制大幅下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-22/chinese-exports-of-battery-material-graphite-plunge-on-controls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北京在本月初实施管制，收紧对先进制造业至关重要的矿物供应的控制后，中国天然石墨（一种用于电动汽车电池的材料）的出口在 12 月份大幅下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-22/chinese-exports-of-battery-material-graphite-plunge-on-controls</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 02:31:40 GMT</pubDate>
